summary: This document is a subpoena issued to Cingular Wireless for subscriber information related to a specific telephone number, covering calls made in September and up to October 5, 2005. It includes instructions for compliance and the potential consequences of failing to appear.

persons.name: Joe Recarey
persons.context: Detective Joe Recarey is mentioned as the contact person for compliance with the subpoena issued to Cingular Wireless.

persons.name: Sharon B.
persons.context: Sharon B. is noted as the Deputy Clerk who witnessed the issuance of the subpoena.

connections.description: Joe Recarey is a detective who works under the jurisdiction of the Palm Beach Police Department, where Sharon B. serves as a Deputy Clerk.

events.title: Subpoena Issued

keyFacts: The subpoena commands Cingular Wireless to provide subscriber information and call records for a specific phone number.
The time frame for the requested information is September 2005 to October 5, 2005.
Failure to comply with the subpoena may result in contempt of court.
The document includes a confidentiality notice regarding the information contained within.
